cd ./webapp
npx supabase start
npx supabase functions serve --no-verify-jwt --env-file supabase/.env
npm run dev


per precommint:
npm run build

deploy function su supabase dev/prod (mettere l'id project )
DEV: npx supabase functions deploy confirm-day --project-ref sjvvnjeotcfdyqlelbck 
PROD: npx supabase functions deploy confirm-day --project-ref lawysreioluscsmjvoft 

Attivare log della function:
npx supabase login
DEV: npx supabase link --project-ref sjvvnjeotcfdyqlelbck
PROD: npx supabase link --project-ref lawysreioluscsmjvoft
npx supabase functions logs confirm-day
 

 Per local verificare:
 Next dev attivo (npm run dev)
Supabase local attivo (supabase start)
Edge function servita in locale (supabase functions serve confirm-day)

Per settare e verificare le variabili per edge function su supabase:
npx supabase functions serve --env-file supabase/.env

npx supabase link --project-ref TUO_DEV_REF
npx supabase secrets set \
  GMAIL_WEBAPP_URL="..." \
  GMAIL_WEBAPP_KEY="..." \
  MAIL_TO_OVERRIDE="..." \
  MAIL_BCC="..."

